After the war, Duessel returned to Grado,[N]
but his days as a general were at an end.[N]
He retired from military service, but not[N]
from leadership. His wisdom was sought[N]
throughout the land, and he served as a[N]
trusted advisor to Grado's new government.[N]
He often sought advice from Renais' General[N]
Seth, having forged an iron-clad friendship[N]
on the battlefield. Their bond served[N]
as a reminder to both nations what their[n]
future could look like.[A][X]